During a game, they might think
about a missed catch

00:03:43.970 --> 00:03:47.306
or how they could bat or bowl better
the next delivery.

00:03:47.848 --> 00:03:51.727
After a game, they might come together
to watch video replays,

00:03:51.769 --> 00:03:54.647
to look at what worked and what didn't,

00:03:54.689 --> 00:03:57.233
which might differ
from what they actually experienced

00:03:57.233 --> 00:03:59.068
during the game itself.

